{"tid":181374,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"工程撚入","createTime":"2017-03-31T14:51:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-20T01:37:34.000Z","uid":50837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d0e0d90c3a6c566bfbc7bbf408573761efd60cb4","tid":181374,"uid":50837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T14:51:18.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟就grad 打算做pc<br />\n但係小弟係度考慮緊做fit out 定起大樓好<br />\n諗左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無巴打可以俾下意見，例如兩者邊個錢途<br />\n好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb2896788f938ae2f2457f700ee49251333c6952","tid":181374,"uid":48326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T14:55:56.000Z","msg":"入maincon 做AE/APC,最好搵個仲起緊石屎廊既盤，一次過學曬起廊同fitting out works"},{"pid":"c46d12d7802b1c32145c184ab8946b550f7abbed","tid":181374,"uid":50837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T15:01:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>入maincon 做AE/APC,最好搵個仲起緊石屎廊既盤，一次過學曬起廊同fitting out works</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打知唔知APC咩價位,兩者升到上去邊個好pay D 其實我最主要都係睇錢做人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48271e9d1f88215c6d7655388931ddc9264d5d26","tid":181374,"uid":50837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T15:05:00.000Z","msg":"其實我驚做左fit out無得返轉頭"},{"pid":"68df0cb909490478d292af93e954d80980e96f7d","tid":181374,"uid":87755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T15:28:59.000Z","msg":"其實做pc好唔好景 好唔好做<br />\n聽人講過pc做極人工都唔會高 又會個個打比你煩住晒<br />\n壓力又大"},{"pid":"c7b0ae39ac39d4c98aaf04c22abf3baab86648d9","tid":181374,"uid":14350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T15:38:59.000Z","msg":"你讀乜竟然想做pc?成撚日比人屌，乜都關你事<br />\nbtw 一定做大樓好話fitout"},{"pid":"568843741f87724d65c7f739db0e652a3173a869","tid":181374,"uid":50837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T16:02:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你讀乜竟然想做pc?成撚日比人屌，乜都關你事<br />\nbtw 一定做大樓好話fitout</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我讀construction management <br />\n點解大樓好過fitout"},{"pid":"45f0d4b0cfd797acc03bef9a134691d3aef8525a","tid":181374,"uid":48326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T04:41:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>入maincon 做AE/APC,最好搵個仲起緊石屎廊既盤，一次過學曬起廊同fitting out works</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打知唔知APC咩價位,兩者升到上去邊個好pay D 其實我最主要都係睇錢做人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇咩學歷出黎。<br />\n1.High dip 就大約16-18k<br />\n2.Degree 就18-22k <br />\n<br />\n視乎咩公司，我上面個range係指main con。"},{"pid":"6e23d63b1fcd7acaa5c12bac01cc13d9e72a0ed9","tid":181374,"uid":48326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T04:45:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實做pc好唔好景 好唔好做<br />\n聽人講過pc做極人工都唔會高 又會個個打比你煩住晒<br />\n壓力又大</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係main con入面做PC，我個人認為係幾好。壓力大唔大就睇你本身做事既能力，如果你係叻仔，所有野都控制得好好既時候，何來壓力？換句話講，要勤力d學好d野，同人打好關係，咁就會做得開心。<br />\n<br />\n人工方面高唔高係主觀既野，如果坐正PC，3萬幾蚊都走唔甩，再升既時候，人工可以去到5-8萬（去到APM,PM級別）"},{"pid":"d8aeb728607ced638a985a502aa3b67271aa2b81","tid":181374,"uid":71725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T07:55:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5449780347ed38c274ddf8d2430bbe9eeaf6fec9","tid":181374,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T08:35:21.000Z","msg":"工程俾狗做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44bf4d7d0a714725782072f8527ac03d01d221ee","tid":181374,"uid":47279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T12:46:44.000Z","msg":"轉行啦 爆喇"},{"pid":"6c62b8892e7bb7203148ab3a53b0e0d69967ef86","tid":181374,"uid":50837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T03:30:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Pc好呀 多野學 人工高 轉工易<br />\n夠料入埋ciob, hkicm，叫價更高</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聽人講ciob 好耐考係咪真"},{"pid":"e3990db89f0606064bf80b7fd1ed7a7aed79425c","tid":181374,"uid":50837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T03:31:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Pc好呀 多野學 人工高 轉工易<br />\n夠料入埋ciob, hkicm，叫價更高</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聽人講ciob 好<span style=\"color: red;\">易</span>考係咪真</blockquote>"},{"pid":"e28d6eb2eae9d61169c984ec4c729ee0b8359ef5","tid":181374,"uid":129825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T01:37:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實做pc好唔好景 好唔好做<br />\n聽人講過pc做極人工都唔會高 又會個個打比你煩住晒<br />\n壓力又大</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係main con入面做PC，我個人認為係幾好。壓力大唔大就睇你本身做事既能力，如果你係叻仔，所有野都控制得好好既時候，何來壓力？換句話講，要勤力d學好d野，同人打好關係，咁就會做得開心。<br />\n<br />\n人工方面高唔高係主觀既野，如果坐正PC，3萬幾蚊都走唔甩，再升既時候，人工可以去到5-8萬（去到APM,PM級別）</blockquote><br />\n記得只做大main con<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做細main con初初同foreman無分別，明明無做錯野都要俾廢老大佬吊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 全場射波射到傻<br />\n利申：玩過幾個月細main con，果排想自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}